  "title": "Senior Accountant / Finance Manager ",
  "description": "<p>Handle full set of accounts including Group consolidation</p><p>Assist in GST, Tax, ACRA fillings in accordance with Singapore Standards and requirements</p><p>Liaise with auditors, tax agent, bankers, company’s secretary and related government boards when necessary</p><p>Handle monthly and annual closing of entities assigned</p><p>Liaise with audit firms and tax consultants on audit and taxation matters, including preparation of audit and tax schedules.</p><p>Preparation of audited financial statements, annual report and Board papers</p><p>Partner closely with subsidiaries finance team for review and analysis of regional subsidiaries’ monthly management accounts</p><p>Preparation of group budgeting</p><p><br /></p><p>Requirements</p><p>Chartered Accountant / ACCA / CPA</p><p>3 to 5 years of related experience in construction or property development industries</p><p></p><p></p><p>E @ mingyan@staffhub.com</p>",
